class pedata.static.example_data.data.ClassificationToyDataset(needed_encodings: list[str] = [])[source]¶

Bases: object

Toy dataset for regression with the needed encodings

__init__(needed_encodings: list[str] = []) → None[source]¶

Initializes a toy dataset for regression with the needed encodings and splits it into train and test splits :param needed_encodings: list of encodings needed for the model.

Defaults to [] -> all encodings are used (see disk_cache.add_encodings).
